*Mostly* cross platform vimrc and plugins. Default setup is for windows, to use with linux, follow these instructions.

clone to ~/.vim/
install pathogen
symlink ~/.vim/bundle -> ~/.vim/vimfiles/bundle
(uses ln -s ~/.vim/vimfiles/bundle ~/.vim/bundle)
copy _vimrc to ~/.vimrc
Edit .vimrc for linux (adjust paths, disable windows specific code)
run find ~/.vim/bundle -follow -exec dos2unix -f '{}' \;

